The Ruby Formula files in this repository describe how to install the axhub CLI
via Homebrew. The Formula source code in this repository is released for the
sole purpose of enabling installation by users with a valid axhub license.

The axhub binary installed by these formulas is governed by the axhub End User
License Agreement (Proprietary) distributed alongside the binary.

Redistribution or modification of the Formula files is permitted only to the
extent necessary to fork and maintain a private tap. Any such derivative must
remove all references to "axhub" and "jocodingax" trademarks.

